<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main>
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header-content">
      <span class="section-tag" style="color:var(--tertiary)">Internal_Manifesto</span>
      <h1>Structure Over Surface</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section" style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-block">
        <h3>Ethos</h3>
        <p>We view garments not as fashion, but as mobile architecture. Every seam, every textile choice, and every silhouette is engineered for the modern urban environment.</p>
        <p>Our process rejects traditional softness in favor of unapologetic utility. The streets demand resilience. We construct gear that acts as both a barrier and an amplifier.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-block">
        <h3>Process</h3>
        <p>Heavyweight canvases, rigid hardware, and high-contrast visuals define our visual language. We don't follow seasons; we issue drops when the prototypes pass our brutal testing protocols. Every design goes through 200+ wear tests before production.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-block">
        <h3>Origin</h3>
        <p>Founded in 2022 between Tokyo and Los Angeles, STREET_ARCHIVE emerged from a frustration with disposable fashion. We wanted garments that could survive years of daily wear without compromising on aesthetics or function.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-stats" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:2rem;margin:4rem 0;text-align:center;">
      <div style="padding:2rem;border:1px solid var(--border);"><span style="font-size:3rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--tertiary);">25</span><p style="color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:0.5rem;">Drops Released</p></div>
      <div style="padding:2rem;border:1px solid var(--border);"><span style="font-size:3rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--tertiary);">12K</span><p style="color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:0.5rem;">Active Holders</p></div>
      <div style="padding:2rem;border:1px solid var(--border);"><span style="font-size:3rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--tertiary);">4.9</span><p style="color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:0.5rem;">Average Rating</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-contact" id="contact">
      <h3>Contact</h3>
      <form action="/contact" method="POST" class="about-form">
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Name" required class="checkout-input">
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" required class="checkout-input">
        <textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Message" required class="checkout-input"></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">Send <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-right"></i></button>
      </form>
      <% if (typeof success !== 'undefined' && success) { %>
        <div class="checkout-success" style="margin-top:1rem;"><%= success %></div>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>